"======================================  The ``v`` module's forward call "
"should accept a batch of observations and return:  ===========  "
"================  ====================================== Symbol       "
"Shape             Description ===========  ================  "
"====================================== ``v``        (batch,)          | "
"Tensor containing the value estimates                                | "
"for the provided observations. (Critical:                                "
