msgstr "任何適用於您提供給 PPO 的 ActorCritic 物件的關鍵字引數。"

#: of spinup.algos.pytorch.ppo.ppo.ppo:55
msgid "Seed for random number generators."
msgstr "隨機數產生器的種子。"

#: of spinup.algos.pytorch.ppo.ppo.ppo:57
msgid ""
"Number of steps of interaction (state-action pairs) for the agent and the"
" environment in each epoch."
msgstr "每個訓練週期 (Epoch) 中代理程式與環境互動的步數（狀態-動作對）。"

#: of spinup.algos.pytorch.ppo.ppo.ppo:60
msgid ""
"Number of epochs of interaction (equivalent to number of policy updates) "
"to perform."
msgstr "要執行的互動訓練週期數（等同於策略更新次數）。"

#: of spinup.algos.pytorch.ppo.ppo.ppo:63
msgid "Discount factor. (Always between 0 and 1.)"
msgstr "折扣因子 (Discount Factor)。（始終介於 0 和 1 之間。）"

#: of spinup.algos.pytorch.ppo.ppo.ppo:65
msgid ""
"Hyperparameter for clipping in the policy objective. Roughly: how far can"
" the new policy go from the old policy while still profiting (improving "
"the objective function)? The new policy can still go farther than the "
"clip_ratio says, but it doesn't help on the objective anymore. (Usually "
"small, 0.1 to 0.3.) Typically denoted by :math:`\\epsilon`."
msgstr ""
"策略目標函數中裁剪的超參數。大致含義：新策略可以偏離舊策略多遠，同時仍能獲益"
"（改善目標函數）？新策略仍可以超出 clip_ratio 所指定的範圍，但不再對目標函數有"
"幫助。（通常較小，0.1 到 0.3。）通常記為 :math:`\\epsilon`。"

#: of spinup.algos.pytorch.ppo.ppo.ppo:72
msgid "Learning rate for policy optimizer."
msgstr "策略優化器的學習率。"

#: of spinup.algos.pytorch.ppo.ppo.ppo:74
msgid "Learning rate for value function optimizer."
msgstr "價值函數 (Value Function) 優化器的學習率。"

#: of spinup.algos.pytorch.ppo.ppo.ppo:76
msgid ""
"Maximum number of gradient descent steps to take on policy loss per "
"epoch. (Early stopping may cause optimizer to take fewer than this.)"
msgstr ""
"每個訓練週期對策略損失函數執行的最大梯度下降步數。（提前停止可能導致優化器執行"
"的步數少於此值。）"

#: of spinup.algos.pytorch.ppo.ppo.ppo:80
msgid "Number of gradient descent steps to take on value function per epoch."
msgstr "每個訓練週期對價值函數執行的梯度下降步數。"

#: of spinup.algos.pytorch.ppo.ppo.ppo:83
msgid "Lambda for GAE-Lambda. (Always between 0 and 1, close to 1.)"
msgstr "廣義優勢估計 (GAE-Lambda) 的 Lambda 值。（始終介於 0 和 1 之間，接近 1。）"

#: of spinup.algos.pytorch.ppo.ppo.ppo:86
msgid "Maximum length of trajectory / episode / rollout."
msgstr "軌跡／回合／展開的最大長度。"

#: of spinup.algos.pytorch.ppo.ppo.ppo:88
msgid ""
"Roughly what KL divergence we think is appropriate between new and old "
"policies after an update. This will get used for early stopping. (Usually"
" small, 0.01 or 0.05.)"
msgstr ""
"大致上我們認為更新後新舊策略之間合適的 KL 散度。這將用於提前停止。（通常較"
"小，0.01 或 0.05。）"

#: of spinup.algos.pytorch.ppo.ppo.ppo:92
msgid "Keyword args for EpochLogger."
msgstr "EpochLogger 的關鍵字引數。"

#: of spinup.algos.pytorch.ppo.ppo.ppo:94
msgid ""
"How often (in terms of gap between epochs) to save the current policy and"
" value function."
msgstr "儲存當前策略和價值函數的頻率（以訓練週期之間的間隔表示）。"

